---
title: Seasoned Shrimp, Salmon and Roasted Potatoes with Feta Salad
description: Garlic, salmon and shrimp aren't the only stars of this dish! Old Bay-seasoned potatoes and a bright, crisp salad topped with salty feta shine through as well. Your tastebuds will be singing!
